data.description: ATTENTION ALL SPORTS FANATICS !!! You will not want to miss seeing this BONUS room/2nd Living/FLEX room/whatever you want to use it for room already set up for your entertaining pleasure!! This well-loved home offers 5 bedrooms with the primary being downstairs and the other 4, bonus/2nd living room/flex room and laundry room being upstairs. All of these bedrooms are OVERSIZED and all have MASSIVE closets. Upon entering the home, you will immediately appreciate how open and spacious this home really is. The kitchen has a large pantry, tons of cabinets and lots of prep space with granite countertops, black appliances to INCLUDE THE FRIDGE with microwave over the range and dishwasher. The dining room, open bar and large living room make it easy to host gatherings and feel like you are still apart of the party with a powder bath conventionally located at the entry.  The attention to design including custom barn doors on the living room windows, the primary windows and the primary bath make this a one of kind find in this community.  If you like to spend time outdoors, you will love the fully fenced backyard with the pergola, extended concrete, firepit, trampoline and playset. And if this isn't enough, the neighborhood has a community park, Veterans park, splash pad and the public library and public schools are within close proximity. Home still has remainder of the 10 Year Structural Warranty.
